WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.190 --> 00:00:02.135
Hello and welcome back,
I am Dr. Rahil Chaudhary.

00:00:02.160 --> 00:00:04.063
Eye doctor, Cataract and
Refractive surgeon.

00:00:04.329 --> 00:00:09.147
In many videos, we have already 
discussed that nowadays...

00:00:09.532 --> 00:00:15.239
with a 10 minutes surgery, 
you can get rid of your specs.

00:00:16.006 --> 00:00:19.499
These surgeries have become
very successful today.

00:00:19.749 --> 00:00:24.868
These surgeries include no pain, no injection, 
no stitches, no blade,

00:00:25.073 --> 00:00:28.605
no cut, no bandage, and no hospitalization.

00:00:28.815 --> 00:00:31.037
From the next day of the surgery,
your vision is fine.

00:00:31.180 --> 00:00:35.521
After one week of precautions, 
the patient can get to their routine.

00:00:36.203 --> 00:00:40.941
So, we now understand that specs removal
is not a big deal in today's time.

00:00:41.439 --> 00:00:45.320
But the only concern is that
these specs removal surgeries...

00:00:45.713 --> 00:00:48.530
are mainly available in private hospitals.

00:00:48.908 --> 00:00:55.313
Except for AIIMS, most government hospitals
do not perform these surgeries.

00:00:55.811 --> 00:00:59.652
And in private hospitals, these surgeries
are usually a bit expensive.

00:00:59.904 --> 00:01:06.412
The cost of these surgeries in case you
remove the specs with a quality surgery like Contoura...

00:01:06.696 --> 00:01:10.696
then the cost of such surgeries come 
around one lakh for both eyes.

00:01:11.058 --> 00:01:17.398
So, patients often ask me if they could get these
surgeries done through government health schemes.

00:01:17.779 --> 00:01:22.803
Like can you take benefit of schemes
such as Ayushman Bharat or Golden card...

00:01:23.030 --> 00:01:26.562
Or many patients are associated
with government panels...

00:01:26.949 --> 00:01:34.350
like some patients are associated with CGHS, DGEHS,
ECHS, ESIC, Haryana government, etc.

00:01:34.496 --> 00:01:36.853
So, can you take some advantage of panel benefits?

00:01:37.146 --> 00:01:39.464
Some people have health insurance...

00:01:39.644 --> 00:01:45.017
or corporate policies and insurance 
from the office where they are working for.

00:01:45.252 --> 00:01:48.569
Or some people also purchase
personal health insurance.

00:01:48.845 --> 00:01:53.559
So, can you benefit from such insurance so that 
you get some relief from the cost of these surgeries?

00:01:53.738 --> 00:01:57.380
Or can you have the Surgery through
these insurances to avoid an extra cost?

00:01:57.646 --> 00:02:01.471
Some people also ask me that 
if they have to spend their own money...

00:02:01.668 --> 00:02:06.462
then is there any EMI facility available so that 
the whole amount is not required to be paid at once?

00:02:06.728 --> 00:02:10.414
And can they make the payment in
the installments within 6-12 months?

00:02:10.605 --> 00:02:12.978
So, I will discuss with you
all these concerns today.

00:02:13.172 --> 00:02:17.180
So, first of all, let's discuss about
Ayushman Bharat or Golden card.

00:02:17.453 --> 00:02:21.620
Look, Ayushman Bharat is a great 
scheme started by the government.

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:26.482
Families with the poor financial condition
can take benefits from this scheme.

00:02:26.821 --> 00:02:33.523
In this scheme, a total of 1350 procedures
are approved by the government...

00:02:33.896 --> 00:02:38.184
to be done from only those hospitals
which are associated with Ayushman Bharat.

00:02:38.651 --> 00:02:43.460
But unfortunately, the specs removal
laser surgeries...

00:02:43.608 --> 00:02:46.656
are not covered in the Ayushman
Bharat scheme.

00:02:46.930 --> 00:02:53.350
And they are not covered because these procedures
fall in the category of cosmetic procedures.

00:02:53.603 --> 00:02:57.547
Cosmetic procedures mean those 
procedures that are not essential.

00:02:58.172 --> 00:03:04.196
Patients have these surgeries for appearance
or because they are tired of wearing specs.

00:03:04.345 --> 00:03:06.464
Or they it done for convenience.

00:03:06.499 --> 00:03:10.008
Because some people want to play sports,
or do adventure activities,

00:03:10.033 --> 00:03:12.619
and the specs are bothering 
them in their routine activities.

00:03:12.885 --> 00:03:15.290
So, for such purposes, a patient
undergo these surgeries.

00:03:15.540 --> 00:03:19.579
Unfortunately, in schemes like
Ayushman Bharat or Golden card...

00:03:19.734 --> 00:03:22.336
all these procedures are 
not approved.

00:03:22.436 --> 00:03:25.483
So, many people are associated
with government panels...

00:03:25.589 --> 00:03:32.259
like CGHS, Central Government Health Scheme,
DGEHS, ESIC, MCD, Haryana Government, etc.

00:03:32.467 --> 00:03:35.650
Different panels operate in our country.

00:03:35.782 --> 00:03:39.520
But again, unfortunately, since these
are cosmetic procedures...

00:03:39.723 --> 00:03:42.461
even government panels don't
cover these.

00:03:42.846 --> 00:03:48.036
However, there is one government panel
which can give you benefits to some extent.

00:03:48.183 --> 00:03:50.390
And that is the panel of the Haryana government.

00:03:50.679 --> 00:03:54.116
Our hospital is associated with 
Haryana government.

00:03:54.318 --> 00:03:59.445
And in the Haryana government panel, 
for these LASIK surgeries or laser procedures...

00:03:59.721 --> 00:04:03.078
you may get the benefit of up to ₹45,000

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:08.264
So, if you are associated with the Haryana
government panel, you can take some benefit out of it.

00:04:08.953 --> 00:04:12.913
Some people ask me that there are
many health insurance policies available...

00:04:13.116 --> 00:04:15.357
you purchase some policies online

00:04:15.382 --> 00:04:20.263
and if you work in corporates, they also provide 
you with some health insurance policies.

00:04:20.655 --> 00:04:23.155
So, there is a lot of variation
in these policies...

00:04:23.460 --> 00:04:28.127
some policies allow your procedure
while some policies don't allow it.

00:04:28.323 --> 00:04:34.077
But we see that a majority of policies give 
approval for the correction of high specs power.

00:04:34.306 --> 00:04:37.258
Like if your specs power is above
-5, -6, or -7...

00:04:37.481 --> 00:04:40.314
then some insurance policies 
give you the cover.

00:04:40.510 --> 00:04:44.764
We also find that some insurance policies
provide you with 100% cover...

00:04:44.904 --> 00:04:48.237
some offer 50% cover, some offer
20% cover...

00:04:48.439 --> 00:04:52.161
so, all this depends on 
what kind of policy you have.

00:04:52.372 --> 00:04:58.769
So, if you want to learn more about this then you should
read your policy completely, everything is mentioned there.

00:04:58.982 --> 00:05:03.656
If you are facing any confusion, then 
you can come to the hospital and discuss it with me.

00:05:03.749 --> 00:05:08.479
And I will help you understand how 
you can take advantage of these policies.

00:05:08.523 --> 00:05:12.166
Next, some people ask me if
there are any EMI options available.

00:05:12.360 --> 00:05:18.188
Since these surgeries are expensive, so is it
possible to make the payment in installments?

00:05:18.367 --> 00:05:20.954
Like installments of 6 months
or 12 months.

00:05:21.163 --> 00:05:24.330
So, yes, this facility is available
in our hospital.

00:05:24.573 --> 00:05:27.780
You don't have to pay the entire
amount at once.

00:05:27.925 --> 00:05:33.631
You can pay in small, comfortable installments
of 6 months, or 12 months.

00:05:33.836 --> 00:05:39.392
Accordingly, you can pay small amounts at
regular intervals and get your procedure done.

00:05:39.595 --> 00:05:43.127
So, our hospital is associated with
BAJAJ FINSERVE.

00:05:43.288 --> 00:05:46.717
And we can provide more information
about this when you come to the hospital.

00:05:47.024 --> 00:05:50.953
So, overall, we can understand that
since these procedures are cosmetic...

00:05:51.108 --> 00:05:56.981
people undergo them for appearance or convenience,
these procedures are not medically essential.

00:05:57.154 --> 00:06:01.844
So, many government panels, Ayushman Bharat,
or many insurances don't cover these procedures.

00:06:01.993 --> 00:06:06.096
Of course, if you are associated with the Haryana panel
or your insurance policy allows it...

00:06:06.307 --> 00:06:11.037
or if you are interested in EMIs, then
through these options, you can lessen your burden.

00:06:11.538 --> 00:06:14.515
Till then, if you have any doubts, 
then you can contact me.

00:06:14.540 --> 00:06:17.794
Thank you very much for watching this video
and I will be back very soon.

